# lldb

> The LLVM Low-Level Debugger
> Help: --help
> More information: https://lldb.llvm.org/man/lldb.html

- Debug an executable:

`lldb "{string some description: executable}"`

- Attach `lldb` to a running process with a specific PID:

`lldb -p {string some description: pid}`

- Wait for a new process to launch with a specific name, and attach to it:

`lldb -w -n "{string some description: process_name}"`
